	affiliation = {Laboratoire d'Automatique et d'Analyse des Systèmes, Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, 7, avenue du Colonel Roche, 31400 Toulouse, France},
	abstract = {If the firing of a transition in a Petri net is considered non instantaneous, it becomes possible to replace a transition in a net P by another net P′ This allows to proceed the description and the analysis of a control structure by stepwise refinements. The necessary and sufficient conditions on P and P′ for the resulting net to be bounded and live, are given. © 1979.},
